WEBVTT

00:01.240 --> 00:05.690
So we’ll have the experience now.

00:05.727 --> 00:07.533
It will take about five minutes

00:07.600 --> 00:10.150
for you because if all the chakras are discussed

00:10.192 --> 00:12.444
already the attention is on that.

00:12.559 --> 00:17.021
Is very simple to put your hands towards Me.

00:17.061 --> 00:21.301
Sahaja Yogi : Everyone steps out his shoes, will you ?

00:28.280 --> 00:30.026
Shri Mataji : It’s better.

00:30.080 --> 00:33.137
[to the Sahaja Yogi] You’ve done a good job Ah

00:33.215 --> 00:36.224
Just put your hands towards Me.

00:36.738 --> 00:39.152
Just like this.

00:39.241 --> 00:43.121
[Shri Mataji takes vibrations of the audience]

00:55.022 --> 00:57.148
Left.

01:08.000 --> 01:11.119
Now, left hand towards Me and right hand towards the Mother Earth.

01:11.175 --> 01:14.558
We’ll give you a balance. You need not close your eyes just now, let’s see.

01:14.606 --> 01:18.560
Put your right hand towards the Mother Earth.

01:19.245 --> 01:23.346
As I told you yesterday left side is our conditioning,

01:23.446 --> 01:26.486
conditioning, subconscious and collective subconscious,

01:26.909 --> 01:28.909
very much at work here.

01:28.974 --> 01:33.093
But also is an emotional side.

01:43.716 --> 01:49.236
Now put your right hand towards Me and left hand towards the sky.

01:49.755 --> 01:53.355
Right hand towards Me, right hand towards Me like this.

01:53.667 --> 01:57.517
Sahaja Yogi : Put your left hand towards the back.

02:09.690 --> 02:13.890
Shri Mataji : Are you feeling the cool breeze in the hand?

02:14.604 --> 02:17.600
You are already thoughtless, there’s no thought,

02:17.683 --> 02:21.746
but just see if you are feeling the cool breeze.

02:25.200 --> 02:27.040
Sahaja Yogi : It’s better [inaudible].

02:27.200 --> 02:29.520
Shri Mataji : Much better

02:29.600 --> 02:31.471
Are you?

02:32.667 --> 02:34.667
Let’s see.

02:35.034 --> 02:41.834
[Shri Mataji blows in the mike].

03:08.490 --> 03:10.490
All right?

03:41.758 --> 03:45.403
Are you feeling any cool breeze in the hand?

03:46.093 --> 03:50.383
All right, now put your left hand on top of your head,

03:51.329 --> 03:53.329
just here,

03:53.508 --> 03:55.964
fontanel bone area.

03:56.898 --> 03:59.167
Are you feeling?

03:59.346 --> 04:01.678
It’s a very subtle thing.

04:03.913 --> 04:05.913
Are you?

04:07.289 --> 04:09.289
Pay attention.

04:11.550 --> 04:14.550
Shri Mataji : [to the Sahaja Yogi]. Working out ; good?

04:14.640 --> 04:17.040
All right. Now, change over.

04:17.080 --> 04:21.500
See the left hand, with the right hand. Just pay attention there, see.

04:30.310 --> 04:32.310
Believe that you are the Spirit.

04:32.510 --> 04:35.157
So just you have to say in your heart: “I am the Spirit”.

04:35.204 --> 04:38.974
In your heart. Say it seven times, it will work out.

04:50.470 --> 04:52.706
Releasing.

04:53.971 --> 04:56.441
Is it all right?

04:56.950 --> 04:59.266
Are you feeling the heat coming out?

04:59.350 --> 05:00.750
Little heat.

05:00.830 --> 05:04.710
All right, now turn, change, see now.

05:09.004 --> 05:11.004
Right Swadhishthan.

05:14.740 --> 05:16.740
All right?

05:16.740 --> 05:18.980
Sahaja Yogi : Right Swadhishthan

05:19.020 --> 05:20.980
Shri Mataji : Left [UNCLEAR]

05:21.625 --> 05:23.625
[Shri Mataji washes her hands with water].

05:23.729 --> 05:28.144
Now, just see, if it is working cool breeze…

05:28.380 --> 05:31.780
[Shri Mataji blows in her hands].

05:33.008 --> 05:37.149
Feel it. Just put your hands like this.

05:48.100 --> 05:50.112
It’s good.

05:51.514 --> 05:55.834
You are all thoughtless. If you see, there’s no thought in your mind.

05:59.314 --> 06:01.594
And complete silence.

06:02.380 --> 06:04.074
Enjoy this.

06:05.300 --> 06:10.740
This moment is going to transform your life, take it from Me.

06:12.010 --> 06:17.690
You may not realize today but you’ll realize it very soon.

06:19.702 --> 06:24.262
Ah, strong.

06:25.424 --> 06:28.824
Have faith in yourself, that’s the main thing.

06:32.984 --> 06:35.754
It’s beautiful.
